organic.title: Ilanka Community Health Center - Native Village of Eyak
organic.snippet: ICHC is a Federally Qualified Health Center that serves all Cordova residents and visitors using our HRSA funded sliding fee scales and Indian Health Services.

organic.title: ICHC: Medical Services - Native Village of Eyak
organic.snippet: We offer a range a services for all ages. From sports physicals to cancer screening, our care teams are committed to providing personalized quality health care.
